node.text:
So, cats will get bored of this pretty quickly...

To make sure that doesn't happen, put some stutter in the movement. 

Like normal speed for ten seconds, hard stop, wigle back and forth maybe?, shoot off at speed, slow back down. 

Idk if you have access to controlling the motors via a single raspberrypi though... Arduino is possible as well, just more complicated.
.
.
.
#catlover #home #catsofinstagram #pets #interiordesign #diy #cute #petsofinstagram
